{"title":"Android开发：如何使用Android Studio进行Debug调试","uid":"4991db212f9d2d78cfd7ddc5a424dc4e","slug":"Android-HowToDebug","date":"2020-04-05T23:59:07.000Z","updated":"2020-05-08T01:40:27.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Android-HowToDebug.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h2 id=\"前提条件\"><a href=\"#前提条件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"前提条件\"></a>前提条件</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>使用Debug首先要建立在你知道你的代码逻辑，知道它的运行顺序以及一些关键点的运行结果是什么。这样Debug才有意义，不然即使你走到那一步，运行的结果不是正确的，但你又不知道应该是什么，结果就这样过去了，所以等于没有Debug。</p></blockquote>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h2 id=\"界面介绍\"><a href=\"#界面介绍\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"界面介绍\"></a>界面介绍</h2><div align=center>\n    <img  src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200408182233.jpg\" >\n</div>\n\n<ul>\n<li>单步跳过<br>点击该按钮将导致程序向下执行一行。如果当前行是一个方法调用，此行调用的方法被执行完毕后再到下一行。（注意不会进入方法内部）</li>\n<li>单步跳入<br>执行该操作将导致程序向下执行一行。如果该行有自定义的方法，则进入该方法内部继续执行，需要注意如果是类库中的方法，则不会进入方法内部。</li>\n<li>强制单步跳入<br>和step into功能类似，主要区别在于：如果当前行有任何方法，则不管该方法是我们自行定义还是类库提供的，都能跳入到方法内部继续执行</li>\n<li>跳到光标所在位置<br>很好用的一个功能，可以忽略所有的断点，跳转到当前光标所在的位置调试；假如我们现在在第8行有断点，第10行有断点，目前程序停留在第8行断点上，我们将光标定位到第9行，单击该按钮，程序将跑到第9行；</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"举例说明\"><a href=\"#举例说明\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"举例说明\"></a>举例说明</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>简要说明一下该程序，主界面中初始显示一个Fragment，该Fragment中有一个按钮，点击后会将Fragment的值通过接口回调给Activity，通过日志打印出来数据。<br>主要代码如下</p></blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><p>MainActivity.java</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\">public class MainActivity extends AppCompatActivity implements LeftFragment.MyListenser &#123;\n    private static final String TAG &#x3D; &quot;MainActivity&quot;;\n    @Override\n    protected void onCreate(Bundle savedInstanceState) &#123;\n        super.onCreate(savedInstanceState);\n        setContentView(R.layout.activity_main);\n    &#125;\n\n    @Override\n    public void setContent(String content) &#123;\n        Log.d(TAG, &quot;setContent: &quot;+content);\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>LeftFragment.java</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\">public class LeftFragment extends Fragment &#123;\n    private static final String TAG &#x3D; &quot;LeftFragment&quot;;\n    private MyListenser myListenser;\n    @Nullable\n    @Override\n    public View onCreateView(@NonNull LayoutInflater inflater, @Nullable ViewGroup container, @Nullable Bundle savedInstanceState) &#123;\n        View view &#x3D; inflater.inflate(R.layout.left_fragment,null);\n        Button button &#x3D; view.findViewById(R.id.button);\n        button.setOnClickListener(new View.OnClickListener() &#123;\n            @Override\n            public void onClick(View v) &#123;\n                myListenser.setContent(&quot;hhhhhhh&quot;);\n            &#125;\n        &#125;);\n        return view;\n    &#125;\n    @Override\n    public void onAttach(Context context) &#123;\n        super.onAttach(context);\n        &#x2F;&#x2F;myListenser &#x3D; (MyListenser) getActivity();\n    &#125;\n    public interface MyListenser&#123;\n        public void setContent(String content);\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>这里我注释了一行代码，模拟写错了，编译运行并没有报错，但是点击按钮后并不会输出数据。下面我们来单步调试找问题。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>代码运行后会有显示按钮，但是点击按钮后直接闪退，这时我们可以看logcat里的error输出的内容，发现是空指针异常。</p>\n<div align=center>\n  <img  src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200408182257.jpg\" >\n</div></li>\n<li><p>大概问题知道了，我们设置断点一点一点找，在点击事件中设置断点，当点击按钮时，进入断点，此时我们发现myListenser这个变量的值为null，所以会发生空指针异常。这样我们就找到了问题所在，只要在onAttach方法中给myListenser赋值就行。</p>\n<div align=center>\n  <img  src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200408182308.jpg\" >\n</div></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"我只是简单写了个例子，实际情况可能更加复杂，具体问题要具体分析。\"><a href=\"#我只是简单写了个例子，实际情况可能更加复杂，具体问题要具体分析。\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"我只是简单写了个例子，实际情况可能更加复杂，具体问题要具体分析。\"></a>我只是简单写了个例子，实际情况可能更加复杂，具体问题要具体分析。</h2>","text":"前提条件 使用Debug首先要建立在你知道你的代码逻辑，知道它的运行顺序以及一些关键点的运行结果是什么。这样Debug才有意义，不然即使你走到那一步，运行的结果不是正确的，但你又不知道应该是什么，结果就这样过去了，所以等于没有Debug。 界面介绍 单步跳过点击该按钮将导致程序向...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.4k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Android","slug":"Android","count":16,"path":"api/categories/Android.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","slug":"Android","count":16,"path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"Debug","slug":"Debug","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Debug.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E6%8F%90%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">前提条件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D\"><span class=\"toc-text\">界面介绍</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%BE%E4%BE%8B%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E\"><span class=\"toc-text\">举例说明</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%88%91%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E5%86%99%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%AA%E4%BE%8B%E5%AD%90%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%9E%E9%99%85%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%9B%B4%E5%8A%A0%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E8%A6%81%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E3%80%82\"><span class=\"toc-text\">我只是简单写了个例子，实际情况可能更加复杂，具体问题要具体分析。</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"CHEN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161140460.jpg","link":"/","description":"学无止境","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/cjpnice","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"Android开发：帧动画，补间动画和属性动画的使用","uid":"e994d11cbe221b873b00a274dd5ec455","slug":"Android-Animation","date":"2020-04-08T00:18:31.000Z","updated":"2020-05-08T01:40:09.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Android-Animation.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"帧动画的使用 在drawable中新建资源文件，使用animation_list定义动画，animation-list定义的动画将顺次从上往下显示item内的图片，设置oneshot=false则反复循环执行，true则执行一次 &lt;?xml version&#x3D;&qu...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"7.4k","symbolsTime":"7 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Android","slug":"Android","count":16,"path":"api/categories/Android.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":25,"path":"api/tags/Java.json"},{"name":"Android","slug":"Android","count":16,"path":"api/tags/Android.json"}],"author":{"name":"CHEN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161140460.jpg","link":"/","description":"学无止境","socials